GMW_CMN_20070107.0009	0	80040.000	80049.900				This is a clear proof that the new birth population in Chinese villages is falling rapidly.	0	0	0		
GMW_CMN_20070107.0009	0	80050.000	80059.900				In many regions in China's countryside, it is already very common to have one child per family; on the contrary, it is rare to see a family raising more than two children.	0	0	0		
