GMW_CMN_20070107.0009	0	110010.000	110019.900				Just as what is said by Professor Qiao Xiaochun of Peking University, "After a country enters the industrialization stage, it is possible to bring down the fertility rate, but it is not quite possible to increase the fertility rate that has already been low for a long time."	0	0	0		
